ame":"avg_npc_254_1#11$1","id":122},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿克托斯","text":"哈哈哈哈，好。","id":123,"figure":["avg_npc_254_1",10],"end":true},{"type":"useless","references":["1","2"],"id":124},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_254_1#1$1","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿克托斯","text":"博士，虽然我只是个粗人，可就连我也看得出来，谢拉格有不寻常的事情在发生。","id":126,"figure":["avg_npc_254_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_254_1#1$1","id":127},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿克托斯","text":"恩希欧迪斯这小子，突然说要还政，又突然把诺希斯赶走，再把你给摆到这个位置上。","id":128,"figure":["avg_npc_254_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_254_1#1$1","id":129},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿克托斯","text":"你又偏偏在处理这个还政时被人袭击了。","id":130,"figure":["avg_npc_254_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_254_1#2$1","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿克托斯","text":"说老实话，我没法不去怀疑恩希欧迪斯，可他也确实没有露出半点破绽。","id":132,"figure":["avg_npc_254_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_254_1#2$1","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿克托斯","text":"但这么不明不白地干等着耶拉冈德交予我们的土地和人民遇险，真叫我不甘心......","id":134,"figure":["avg_npc_254_1",1]},{"type":"dialog","id":135},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_254_1#2$1","focus":"-1","id":136},{"type":"decision","options":[{"id":"138","text":"那么，阿克托斯先生......"}],"values":[],"id":137},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":138,"end":140},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_254_1#4$1","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿克托斯","text":"怎么了？","id":140,"figure":["avg_npc_254_1",3],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":141},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_254_1#4$1","focus":"-1","id":142},{"type":"decision","options":[{"id":"144","text":"我们的和解也可能意味着......"},{"id":"144","text":"如果对手能预想到你的反应就说明......"}],"values":[],"id":143},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":144},{"type":"decision","options":[{"id":"146","text":"对手不再需要拿我充当障眼法了。"},{"id":"146","text":"对手已经准备完毕，时间不多了。"}],"values":[],"id":145},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":146,"end":148},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_254_1#7$1","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿克托斯","text":"什么？！","id":148,"figure":["avg_npc_254_1",6],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":149},{"type":"character","id":150},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":151},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_explo_n","volume":"0.6","id":152},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":153},{"type":"text","text":"“轰”的一声，巨大的闷响在远处炸开。","id":154},{"type":"text","text":"屋外的人交头接耳，讨论着是不是要下雪了。","id":155},{"type":"text","text":"屋里的人低头不语，肩负着没有实体的重压。","id":156},{"type":"dialog","id":157},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":158},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":159},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":160},{"type":"character","id":161},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/88/Avg_bg_24_g8_nobleroom.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":162},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":163},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness02_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness02_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":164,"musicid":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":165},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":166},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#1$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1","fadetime":"0.7","id":167},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":168},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#1$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":169},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈塔托丝","text":"诺希斯·埃德怀斯阁下。","id":170,"figure":["avg_npc_253_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#1$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺希斯","text":"菈塔托丝·布朗陶大人。","id":172,"figure":["avg_206_gnosis_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#1$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺希斯","text":"看来，我终于获得了与你当面交谈的资格，是吗？","id":174,"figure":["avg_206_gnosis_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#1$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈塔托丝","text":"那副佯装出来的傲气并不能隐瞒什么，诺希斯。","id":176,"figure":["avg_npc_253_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#1$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈塔托丝","text":"你也是个聪明人，我们明人不说暗话。","id":178,"figure":["avg_npc_253_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#1$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈塔托丝","text":"要不是想从我这里得到什么，你根本不会像这样一而再，再而三地来访。","id":180,"figure":["avg_npc_253_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#1$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":181},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺希斯","text":"呵，如果你只是想宣示自己掌握着主动权，那么我想我该告辞了。","id":182,"figure":["avg_206_gnosis_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#1$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":183},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈塔托丝","text":"别急，诺希斯，我有一些问题想要向你讨教。","id":184,"figure":["avg_npc_253_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#1$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈塔托丝","text":"当我第一次听说埃德怀斯家的人跟着恩希欧迪斯回到了谢拉格时，老实说，我不太吃惊。","id":186,"figure":["avg_npc_253_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#1$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈塔托丝","text":"我以为你掌握了能够证明埃德怀斯家不曾加害希瓦艾什家的证据，或者，你抓住了恩希欧迪斯的把柄。","id":188,"figure":["avg_npc_253_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#1$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈塔托丝","text":"但无论你还是恩希欧迪斯都缄口不谈当年之事，任由希瓦艾什家的领民痛骂你厚颜无耻。","id":190,"figure":["avg_npc_253_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#10$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈塔托丝","text":"究竟是什么在支撑着你？我很好奇。","id":192,"figure":["avg_npc_253_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#10$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":193},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺希斯","text":"......他曾向我许诺一个未来。","id":194,"figure":["avg_206_gnosis_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#1$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈塔托丝","text":"未来？","id":196,"figure":["avg_npc_253_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#1$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺希斯","text":"谢拉格的未来。一个能让我在研究中施展才学而不必担心成果被剽窃、滥用、埋没的新兴工业科技国家。","id":198,"figure":["avg_206_gnosis_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#7$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈塔托丝","text":"仅仅是这样？","id":200,"figure":["avg_npc_253_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#7$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺希斯","text":"所以我一开始就并不指望你能够理解，菈塔托丝，你永远也不会成为一名研究者。","id":202,"figure":["avg_206_gnosis_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#7$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":203},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺希斯","text":"你可能很难理解，有着充足的资源与权力支持，又有着正当的目的，在完全安心的前提下探索技术的创新与应用会有多么令人心醉。","id":204,"figure":["avg_206_gnosis_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#1$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈塔托丝","text":"所以你们是达成了一项交易。你向他提供技术，他为你提供舞台。","id":206,"figure":["avg_npc_253_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#1$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈塔托丝","text":"然后呢？","id":208,"figure":["avg_npc_253_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#1$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":209},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈塔托丝","text":"你应该不会是想告诉我，他真的就只是为了保全自身，要把你推出来当替死鬼。","id":210,"figure":["avg_npc_253_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#1$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":211},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈塔托丝","text":"你们喀兰贸易对利害的权衡不会只有这种程度吧？","id":212,"figure":["avg_npc_253_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#1$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺希斯","text":"你对喀兰贸易倒是充满信心。两年前何不接受邀请，向恩希欧迪斯投诚呢？","id":214,"figure":["avg_206_gnosis_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#7$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈塔托丝","text":"少说蠢话。恩希欧迪斯纵有天大的本事，也没法改变这千年来深入谢拉格人骨髓里的信仰。","id":216,"figure":["avg_npc_253_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#7$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":217},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈塔托丝","text":"喀兰贸易只能生长到它被三族议会和蔓珠院允许的大小，谢拉格根本不可能变成什么工业科技国家——","id":218,"figure":["avg_npc_253_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#2$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":219},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈塔托丝","text":"——等等。","id":220,"figure":["avg_npc_253_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#1$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":221},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈塔托丝","text":"所以他找到新筹码了？","id":222,"figure":["avg_npc_253_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#1$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺希斯","text":"你说得对。","id":224,"figure":["avg_206_gnosis_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#1$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":225},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺希斯","text":"恩希欧迪斯没有办法让谢拉格人违背耶拉冈德，他只能找到一个平衡点。","id":226,"figure":["avg_206_gnosis_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#1$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":227},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺希斯","text":"但他已经在这个平衡点停滞了太久。哪怕我几次三番试图推动他，他也无动于衷。","id":228,"figure":["avg_206_gnosis_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#1$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":229},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺希斯","text":"直到事情终于出现了转机。","id":230,"figure":["avg_206_gnosis_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#1$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺希斯","text":"恩希亚的矿石病症状得到了控制，尽管无法治愈，但她已经能活蹦乱跳地回到他的身边......","id":232,"figure":["avg_206_gnosis_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#1$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺希斯","text":"并且兴奋地告诉他，或许可以拓宽与对方的合作，用更低廉的成本，更好地控制住矿石病的扩散和危害。","id":234,"figure":["avg_206_gnosis_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#5$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":235},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈塔托丝","text":"不，恩希欧迪斯他不会......","id":236,"figure":["avg_npc_253_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#2$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":237},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺希斯","text":"他当然会。谢拉格的国门一旦打开，就不可能再完全封闭。","id":238,"figure":["avg_206_gnosis_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#2$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺希斯","text":"谢拉格的感染者数量只会日渐增加，这是大地诸国的客观情况，在谢拉格不断发展的过程中，处理矿石病的能力终将成为新的筹码。","id":240,"figure":["avg_206_gnosis_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#2$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":241},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺希斯","text":"他即将让谢拉格人在信仰与技术中选择一个，而仅凭信仰已经不再能保护他们远离矿石病。","id":242,"figure":["avg_206_gnosis_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#7$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":243},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈塔托丝","text":"......空口无凭，你说的这些都没有证据。","id":244,"figure":["avg_npc_253_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_253_1#7$1","name2":"avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":245},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诺希斯","text":"......跟我来吧，带上你的人，多带点能打的，我给你看一些东西。","id":246,"figure":["avg_206_gnosis_1",8]},{"type":"dialog","id":247},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":248},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":249},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":250},{"type":"character","id":251},{"type":"image","id":252}],"characters":["迟钝的战士","多事的战士","瓦莱丝","？？？","阿克托斯","菈塔托丝","诺希斯"]}